	<preparation>Cream together shortening, sugar and vanilla.  Add chips and nuts.  Stir in flour and  a pinch of salt.  Chill dough to slightly firm.

Form dough into small balls and press flat.  Sprinkle cookes with sugar using a fork and bake at 350F until light brown.  </preparation>
